1.0.4 - 05/14/08
     Fixed sort arrows display when using Mod_Rewrite
     Fixed IP Lookup Link when using Mod_Rewrite

1.0.3 - 05/13/08
	Added Sort Options to User Info Tab
	Added Pagination to User Info Tab
	Added setup option to set the # Per Page
	Added setup option to set the Default Sort Column
	Added setup option to set the Default Sort Order
	Added setup option to set the Date/Time Display
	     Can be different than the General Date/Time Display

